The issue is in the chat command where some operations are commented out and the session state is being mishandled. Here's the fix:

index.ts
Fix the session ending logic to properly save all messages and state:

index.ts
The key changes are:

Uncomment the resolution message save
Save the session before breaking
Update the in-memory session map
Add explicit save when continuing
Fix the session state handling during resolution
This should prevent the file from being overwritten with blank space when ending the session.
